Class BpProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ihealth.communication.control.BpProfile

  • public class BpProfile
extends java.lang.Object
    Public APIs for the Bp serials device profiles

    Clients need to calliHealthDevicesManager.registerClientCallback(com.ihealth.communication.manager.iHealthDevicesCallback) register. When new data from Bp device, The Callback{#iHealthDevicesCallback #onDeviceNotify} can be triggered should call.

      • ERROR_NUM_BP

        public static final java.lang.String ERROR_NUM_BP
        The key of error ID number of BP device.

        Flag Error number of Bp device.

          Error code and Description

          0:not find a suitable zero in 20s.

          1:not find high pressure.

          2:not find low pressure or the high pressure value is lower than the low pressure value.

          3:pressurization fast.

          4:pressurization slow.

          5:pressure exceeds 300mmHg.

          6:time of pressure greater than 15 mmHg exceeds 160s.

          7:EE read and write error.

          8:EE three backup data error.

          9:retention.

          10:SPAN value error.

          11:CRC errors.

          12:connect error.

          13:low power tips.

          14:high or low pressure value of measurement exceeds the set upper limit.

          15:high or low pressure value of measurement exceeds the set lower limit.

          16:arm movement during the measurement over the machine set point.

          400:the argument of method is illegal.

          401:the operation is illegal.

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

              • FUNCTION_OPERATING_STATE_ABPM

                public static final java.lang.String FUNCTION_OPERATING_STATE_ABPM
                The function information:The last time measure status.

                Description of last measure status.

                  0:not find a suitable zero in 20s.

                  1:not find high pressure.

                  2:not find low pressure or the high pressure value is lower than the low pressure value.

                  3:pressurization fast.

                  4:pressurization slow.

                  5:pressure exceeds 300mmHg.

                  6:time of pressure greater than 15 mmHg exceeds 160s.

                  7:EE read and write error.

                  8:EE three backup data error.

                  9:retention.

                  10:SPAN value error.

                  11:CRC errors.

                  12:connect error.

                  13:low power tips.

                  14:high or low pressure value of measurement exceeds the set upper limit.

                  15:high or low pressure value of measurement exceeds the set lower limit.

                  16:arm movement during the measurement over the machine set point.

                  85:the message of correct or error operation has been send to APP.
